              <h2 className="headline text-[clamp(1.6rem,4.5vw,2.6rem)] text-primary leading-[0.95] mb-3">TRUSTED BY INDUSTRIES.<br /><span className="text-secondary">PARTNERED FOR PROGRESS.</span></h2>
              <p className="text-sm text-text-muted">Across continents and industries, we build more than machines — we build long-term partnerships.</p>
